ary policies  strategies and structures of international businesses  and how basic business functions are best performed on an international basis  Prerequisite s  EC 201  EC 202    Back to Top   Print Friendly Page   All catalogues   2016 Virginia Military Institute  Powered by the Acalog  Academic Catalog Management System   ACMS  Mobile Site 